data.description: This is a 3 bedroom 2 bath pool home with a new roof and has been newly painted in 2019.  It has an open floor and off of the kitchen is a family room with a door that leads out to a covered patio.  You can enjoy the patio after a swim in the pool and there's a large back yard for all of your barbecue parties.  Conveniently located to all shopping and restaurants.  This house is perfect for a first time home buyer.  Call today to schedule an appointment to see this property.
